{"tid":436680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇見過耶教徒聯群結隊去玩哈佬喂？","createTime":"2017-10-15T10:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T15:51:08.000Z","uid":21558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"516eb01a75b0a1291faa97a28111a14070ba65b7","tid":436680,"uid":21558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"話說上星期去哈佬喂<br />\n點知撞到大學同學<br />\n最好笑係呢個大學同學係耶教徒<br />\n佢見到我時，仲好如常同我打招呼<br />\n但我又衰多口<br />\n衝口而出講左句心入面果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇諗到係呢度見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個同學面色一變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講左兩句就走左<br />\n<br />\n講完一大輪，其實我係想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解會有耶教徒咁虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日口口聲聲話唔會慶祝萬聖節<br />\n但自己又走去哈佬喂玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5344d3f44fe023a4b704bf48f90a7168b445570f","tid":436680,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"異教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1fa68c9ecea8ebc9774c3a3bf11a05b1f0bef2","tid":436680,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"香港啲耶撚多數都偽耶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d307d2d7db9386701183acbf70e9f3c09975a46","tid":436680,"uid":21558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-